Package: riborex
Type: Package
Title: Identification of differential translation from Ribo-seq data
Version: 2.3.4
Date: 2016-07-11
Author: Wenzheng Li, Weili Wang and Andrew D. Smith
Maintainer: Wenzheng Li <wenzhenl@usc.edu>
Description: Fast and flexible identification of differentially translated
             genes from Ribo-seq data using existing RNA-seq analysis
             methods as engines
License: GPL-3
Depends: DESeq2, edgeR, fdrtool
